            "title": "《專訪》－－大摩：中國貸款息低礙反內捲",
            "description": "<p id=\"date\">2025年12月22日</p>\n<p class=\"info\">\t\n<span class=\"column\"><a href=\"https://search.hkej.com/template/fulltextsearch/php/search.php?q=專訪\">專訪</a></span>\n</p>\n    <h1 id=\"article-title\" class=\"sub_ex_article-title\">大摩：中國貸款息低礙反內捲<br>    \n   \n    </h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2025/12/22/4279082_7fb194d07680e8ba9e526b70f82a3b16.jpg\" title=\"摩根士丹利中國金融行業研究主管_徐然（黃潤根攝）\" class=\"thickbox\"><img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2025/12/22/4279082_7fb194d07680e8ba9e526b70f82a3b16_620.jpg\" border=\"0\"></a></p>\n<span class='enlargeImg'><a href=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2025/12/22/4279082_7fb194d07680e8ba9e526b70f82a3b16.jpg\" title=\"摩根士丹利中國金融行業研究主管_徐然（黃潤根攝）\" class=\"thickbox\"><img src='https://static.hkej.com/hkej/ejweb/enlarge.gif' align='absmiddle' />放大圖片</a> / <a href=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2025/12/22/4279082_7fb194d07680e8ba9e526b70f82a3b16.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"摩根士丹利中國金融行業研究主管_徐然（黃潤根攝）\">顯示原圖</a></span>\n<p></p>\n在內地經濟增長放緩的背景下，近年人民銀行接連減息，同時指導銀行加快放貸，以支持實體經濟。不過，摩根士丹利中國金融行業研究主管徐然指出，銀行貸款利率下降，比政策利率下降得更多。當利率過低，淘汰落後產能效率也會較低，導致產能更加過剩，坦言現在利率降到這麼低，恐已「弊大於利」，合理的貸款定價會有利於反內捲...\n<p>（節錄）</p>",
            "link": "https://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/headline/article/4279082/%E5%A4%A7%E6%91%A9%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%B2%B8%E6%AC%BE%E6%81%AF%E4%BD%8E%E7%A4%99%E5%8F%8D%E5%85%A7%E6%8D%B2",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-22 03:10:42",
            "source": "hkej",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
